$ scalr-tools_

  Scalr-tools is a command-line interface to your Scalr account

  Version 2.0 is intended to work with the new Scalr JSON API. 

Usage:

  $ pip install --editable .
  $ scalr-tools --help


To setup bash completion permanently put this into your bashrc instead:

. /path/to/pecha/scalr-tools-complete.sh

or run

eval "$(_SCALR_TOOLS_COMPLETE=source scalr-tools)"

